Package io.micronaut.data.intercept.annotation

Annotation Type DataMethod

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target({METHOD,ANNOTATION_TYPE})
@Internal
@Inherited
public @interface DataMethod
    Internal annotation used to configure execution handling for DataIntroductionAdvice.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    graemerocher
